channel.title: My first week with Photoshop
channel.description:
Hey guys, this is a summary of my first week working with Photoshop, some of these sigs (most of em) I've already shown you, but theres some new ones too... (Newest sig is at the bottom.) Rate and comment.
[img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/1st%20Sig.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Sig2.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Firefox.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Girl.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/RS%20Buddies.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Naruto%20v2.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Once%20Dead.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Cutting%20Blade.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.freewebs.com/meesig/Ghostrider.jpg[/img]
Kinda productive week eh? :) Well, the first three signatures I made without any tutorials or help, maybe some tips from when i shown them here;) And the rest was made using some tuts from "O M G", "Kaza", "Fellixombc" and "The Wise Guy" Big creds ;) Enjoy.. :cool:
